      "zh": "由 Avon 防护公司制造的防毒面具，专为竞标美军联合勤务通用面具 (JSGPM) 计划而设计。该项目旨在为执行特殊任务的行动人员提供全面核生化防护，同时尽可能采用轻量化设计，以确保在多种行动条件下的穿戴舒适度。",
      "en": "The gas mask from Avon Protection was developed under the JSGPM (Joint Service General Purpose Mask) program to provide special operations forces with maximum protection against CBRN threats while keeping the design lightweight and comfortable for use in a wide range of conditions."
